<p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center;line-height:37px"><br/></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">一、报考条件</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">已完成江西省</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">2024年普通高考报名的考生均可报考。尚未完成高考报名的</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">，</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">可于</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">2月26</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">日</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">—</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">28日到户籍或毕业学校所在县</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">（</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">市、区</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">）</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">招办办理补报名手续。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">二、报名时间及方式</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">（一）报名时间：</span></p><p style="text-indent:93px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">3月7日9:00--3月9日17:00。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">（二）</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">报名方式：</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">考生在规定时间内自行登陆江西省教育考试院网（网址</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">www.jxeea.cn）“高职单招报考系统”，签订《江西省2024年高职单招考试诚信报考承诺书》，按照网页提示的操作流程进入网报系统，选报江西软件职业技术大学（院校代码8618）。</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">在专业选择页面，考生可填报</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">不超过</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">6个专业</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">，</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">并勾选是</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">否服从专业调剂。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">三、</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">2024年单招招生专业及计划</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240225/1708854492849059503.png" title="1708854492849059503.png" alt="f7e136c57011ef9fee068564f36cd46.png"/></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">注意：我校</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">002专业组的专业仅限已完成江西省2024年普通高考报名且是退役士兵的考生报考，</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">非退役士兵考生</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">不得</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">报考</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px"><br clear="all" style="page-break-before:always"/></span> </p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">四、准考证领取</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">（一）考生在</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">3月14日9</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">:</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">00起可登录学校官网查询考场安排信息，3月17日8</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">:</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">00前到学校现场领取准考证、熟悉考场等。考生须携带身份证和准考证参加考试。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">（二）报考了第</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">002专业组专业的考生需于3月15日18</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">:</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">00前到校现场审核退役证书原件，并提交身份证复印件和退役证书复印件，通过资格审查后可取得考试资格。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">（三）准考证发放地址：江西软件职业技术大学行政楼一楼大厅接待处。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">五、考试安排</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">高职单招考试由我校自行组织实施，省考试院全程监督，采取</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">“文化素质+职业技能测试”考试两部分，总分满分为450分，其中文化素质考试科目为：语文、数学并卷200分</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">；</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">职业技能测试</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">250分。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">（一）考试时间：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">3月17日（星期日）</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">9</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">:00-12:00</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">（二）考试地点：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">D11教学楼</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">六、录取工作</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">（一）录取原则</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">严格</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">按照</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">教育部、省教育厅等部门要求，全面实施阳光招生，根据招生计划及考生总成绩排名，按</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">“专业志愿优先”原则录取</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">。</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">如遇考生总成绩相同时，依次看职业技能测试、数学、语文单科成绩。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">对填报的专业计划已录取满额且专业服从调剂的考生，按</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">江西省</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">教育厅有关规定</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">，</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">学校</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">可在该专业组缺额的招生专业中进行调剂录取</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">。</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">对专业不服从调剂的考生，但所填专业录取额满，考生可向</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">学校</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">提出专业服从调剂的申请，经</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">学校</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">同意后，可在该专业组缺额的专业中进行调剂录取，否则作退档处理。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">专业组之间不可调剂录取</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">，</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">各专业组如有缺额计划将按省教育厅有关规定内调至其他生源充足的专业组顺延录取。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">（二）优惠政策</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">高职单招优惠政策按照《江西省关于进一步深化高考加分改革的实施方案》（赣招委字〔</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">2019〕25号）执行。在校学习期间获得“江西省职业院校技能大赛”三等奖以上的应届毕业生，可按照省教育厅规定的程序申请免试就读高职院校相同或相近专业。免试录取工作在高职单招录取前完成。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">退役士兵考生加分</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">20分，直接计入总成绩。</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">符合国家教育资助政策的退役士兵考生，报考第</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">002专业组专业被录取报到后，可申请减免学费和书本费、住宿费等杂费。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">（三）自动放弃</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">预录取考生如因自身原因需放弃录取资格，须在预录取名单公布后</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">2个工作日到校招生部门现场提交放弃申请，经学校单独招生工作领导小组批准后，取消其录取资格。未在规定时间内办理的，所造成的后果由考生自行承担。因考生放弃所产生的缺额不实行递补。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">（四）录取名单公示</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">根据录取原则，确定拟录考生名单，经学校单独招生工作小组审批后，在江西软件职业技术大学官网公示，正式录取数据严格按省厅文件要求完成相关手续备案。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">（五）录取通知书发放</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">考生录取数据</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">经</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">江西省教育厅相关部门的审批通过后，正式公布录取名单，发放录取通知书。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">七、其他注意事项</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">（一）通过高职单招录取的考生，与参加统一高考录取的考生享受相同待遇。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">（二）考生经高职单招录取后，不再具有参加普通高考及录取资格。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">（三）考生被高职单招录取后，不得更换专业，也不能退录。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">（四）所有录取考生，根据学校教学安排，需前往井冈山数字经济产业学院参加实践教学。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">（五）未尽事宜或与上级部门相关政策规定冲突，以上级部门相关政策规定为准。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">八、联系方式及来校路线</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">咨询电话：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">0791-83792888</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 0791-83792998</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">薛老师</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">15579166678</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">（</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">微信同号</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">）</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">胡老师</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">15270569149</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">（</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">微信同号</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">）</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">来校路线：市内公交车乘坐</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">143（起点红谷滩配套中心）、136（起点八一桥下塘子河停车场）路公交车至江西软件职业技术大学站下车。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:right;line-height:36px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">江西软件职业技术大学</span></p><p style="text-align: right; line-height: 36px;"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">2024年2月2</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">5</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">日</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p>